#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: plogins-proof.php
msgid "Proof - Sales Notifications for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Proof – Verkaufsbenachrichtigungen für WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: plogins-proof.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/proof/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/de/proof/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: plogins-proof.php
msgid "Show recent-sale social-proof popups to build trust and urgency."
msgstr ""
"Zeige Social-Proof-Popups aus aktuellen Verkäufen an, um Vertrauen und "
"Dringlichkeit aufzubauen."

#. Author of the plugin
#: plogins-proof.php
msgid "WPPoland"
msgstr "WPPoland"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: plogins-proof.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/"

#: plogins-proof.php:48
msgid ""
"Proof - Sales Notifications for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to be "
"active."
msgstr ""
"Proof – Verkaufsbenachrichtigungen für WooCommerce erfordert, dass "
"WooCommerce aktiv ist."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:44 src/Admin/Settings.php:102
msgid "Proof: Sales Notifications"
msgstr "Proof: Verkaufsbenachrichtigungen"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:45
msgid "Proof"
msgstr "Proof"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:103
msgid ""
"Show small popups of recent real purchases to build trust and urgency. Only "
"a first name and city are ever shown, never full names, emails or addresses."
msgstr ""
"Zeige kleine Popups der letzten echten Käufe an, um Vertrauen und "
"Dringlichkeit aufzubauen. Es werden immer nur Vorname und Stadt angezeigt, "
"niemals vollständige Namen, E-Mails oder Adressen."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:112
msgid "Save changes"
msgstr "Änderungen speichern"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:123
msgid "General"
msgstr "Allgemein"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:128
msgid "Enable Proof"
msgstr "Proof aktivieren"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:129
msgid ""
"Master switch. When off, no popups are loaded or rendered anywhere on the "
"storefront."
msgstr ""
"Hauptschalter. Wenn diese Option deaktiviert ist, werden nirgendwo in der "
"Storefront Popups geladen oder gerendert."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:135
msgid "Screen corner"
msgstr "Bildschirmecke"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:137
msgid "Bottom left"
msgstr "Unten links"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:138
msgid "Bottom right"
msgstr "Unten rechts"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:139
msgid "Top left"
msgstr "Oben links"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:140
msgid "Top right"
msgstr "Oben rechts"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:143
msgid "Which corner of the screen the popup slides in from."
msgstr "Aus welcher Ecke des Bildschirms das Popup eingeblendet wird."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:156
msgid "What each popup shows"
msgstr "Was jedes Popup zeigt"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:157
msgid ""
"Each popup shows the buyer's first name, billing city, the product name and "
"how long ago the purchase happened. Surnames, emails and full addresses are "
"never shown."
msgstr ""
"In jedem Popup werden der Vorname des Käufers, der Ort der "
"Rechnungsstellung, der Produktname und die Zeit angezeigt, vor der der Kauf "
"getätigt wurde. Nachnamen, E-Mail-Adressen und vollständige Adressen werden "
"niemals angezeigt."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Fallback name"
msgstr "Fallback-Name"

#. translators: %s is the default fallback word shown when an order has no
#. first name.
#: src/Admin/Settings.php:168
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Shown in place of a first name when the order has none. Leave blank to use "
"the default, %s."
msgstr ""
"Wird anstelle eines Vornamens angezeigt, wenn die Bestellung keinen enthält."
" Lass das Feld leer, um den Standardwert %s zu verwenden."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:181
msgid "Timing"
msgstr "Timing"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:184
msgid "Initial delay (seconds)"
msgstr "Anfängliche Verzögerung (Sekunden)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:184
msgid ""
"How long to wait after the page loads before the first popup appears. "
"Default 5 seconds."
msgstr ""
"Wie lange nach dem Laden der Seite gewartet werden soll, bevor das erste "
"Popup erscheint. Standardmäßig 5 Sekunden."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:185
msgid "Display time (seconds)"
msgstr "Anzeigezeit (Sekunden)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:185
msgid ""
"How long each popup stays on screen before sliding away. Default 6 seconds."
msgstr ""
"Wie lange jedes Popup auf dem Bildschirm bleibt, bevor es verschwindet. "
"Standardmäßig 6 Sekunden."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:186
msgid "Interval between popups (seconds)"
msgstr "Intervall zwischen Popups (Sekunden)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:186
msgid ""
"Gap between one popup disappearing and the next appearing. Lower values show"
" more popups; higher values feel calmer. Default 12 seconds."
msgstr ""
"Lücke zwischen dem Verschwinden eines Popups und dem Erscheinen des "
"nächsten. Niedrigere Werte zeigen mehr Popups an; Höhere Werte fühlen sich "
"ruhiger an. Standardmäßig 12 Sekunden."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:199
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Beispiel"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:206
msgid "Alex from Berlin"
msgstr "Alex aus Berlin"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:206
msgid "bought Merino Hoodie"
msgstr "Merino Hoodie gekauft"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:207
msgid "2 hours ago"
msgstr "Vor 2 Stunden"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:224
msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "Aktiviert"

#: src/Service/FrontendService.php:87
msgid "Recent purchase"
msgstr "Kürzlich gekauft"

#: src/Service/FrontendService.php:88
msgid "Dismiss notification"
msgstr "Benachrichtigung verwerfen"

#. translators: connects a name to a city, e.g. "Alex from Berlin".
#: src/Service/FrontendService.php:90
msgid "from"
msgstr "von"

#. translators: connects a buyer to a product, e.g. "bought Hoodie".
#: src/Service/FrontendService.php:92
msgid "bought"
msgstr "gekauft"

#: src/Service/OrderFeed.php:124
msgid "Someone"
msgstr "Jemand"

#. translators: %s: human-readable time difference, e.g. "2 hours".
#: src/Service/OrderFeed.php:171
#, php-format
msgid "%s ago"
msgstr "Vor %s"
